data.text: @Casillic Have seen a few people posting online about how difficult it is to access testing in the US. Its quite the opposite here!
@Casillic Would you believe that here in Belfast, you could just walk into the sports centre near my house and lift as many as you wanted off a table in the hallway?
@Casillic How long were you waiting on it arriving?

@Casillic There are infamous levels of false positives (and some false negatives) with the kits.
Even what you eat or drink, and temperatures can affect results.
